    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid project or a budget-friendly daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior has some noticeable dings, fading clear coat on the roof, and a few minor scuffs on the bumpers. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear and a few stains, though it remains functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives, but it will likely need suspension work and a tune-up in the near future to ensure long-term reliability.",
