    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a car with potential? This vehicle has seen plenty of adventures and is ready for a new owner who isn't afraid of a little TLC! While it shows significant wear and will need some mechanical and cosmetic work to get back to its best, it's a great opportunity for a handy DIYer to breathe new life into a classic ride!",
